Package: kiWisConnect
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Accessing and Exporting KIWIS Time Series Data for AquaZIS or Other Uses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Marcel", 
           family = "Gaj", 
           email = "marcel.gaj@lanuv.nrw.de", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides functions to query KIWIS hydrological time series data and export them in ZRXP format
    compatible with AquaZIS. Includes tools to retrieve time series metadata, download values with
    automatic batching for large datasets, and prepare data for AquaZIS import.
